Simple to install!!!
Just copy the contents of the current directory to ~/.alerts
add wallpaper_generator to auto-start programs
edit the tasks/tasks file to set one task on one line
run python code as : python wallpaper_generator.py

Requirements:
GNOME - 3
Python - 3
Image Magik


Improvements to come:
  1) UI to add new tasks
  2) easy installer
PS: You are free to contribute to this project.


